The standard location of the keyboard

/etc/default/keyboard

 All available keyboard models.
 
 /usr/share/X11/xkb/rules/xorg.lst
 
 Install keyboard indicator utility 
 
 sudo apt-get install fbxkb  
 
 Go into windows manager autostart.
 
 .config/i3/autostart.sh
 
 Edit sxhkd config file.
 
 vim ~/.config/i3/sxhkd/sxhkdrc
 nano ~/.config/i3/sxhkd/sxhkdrc
 nvim ~/.config/i3/sxhkd/sxhkdrc
 gedit ~/.config/i3/sxhkd/sxhkdrc
 
 and add the following commands

#keyboard switch to us layout or latam layout

alt + shift 

setxkbmap 'us'
setxkbmap 'latam'



 
